cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is about image reconstruction using a variant of conditional generative adversarial networks (conditional GANs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel generator and multi-scale discriminators, which are related to machine learning and deep learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of adversarial losses and corresponding point loss also suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as a possible category. The paper also mentions image inpainting and image recovery from polluted blocks, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
